title: DeepSeek’s latest open-source AI models land to challenge GPT-5 and Gemini 3.0 Pro
description: DeepSeek is back with new open-source AI models: DeepSeek V3.2 and V3.2-Speciale. These are said to challenge both OpenAI and Google's creations. Here's what is known about them to date.
content:
After taking the world by storm and sending the US stock markets tumbling in January 2025, DeepSeek has now announced two new open-source AI models: DeepSeek V3.2 and DeepSeek V3.2-Speciale.
